      <title>个人博客第二篇——下载Git</title>
      <link href="/posts/second.html"/>
      <url>/posts/second.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p><a href="/posts/7d37f72d.html">返回</a></p></blockquote><h1 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h1><p><font size=4; color=red>(已经装有Git的请忽略此步骤)</font></p><blockquote><p><font size=4>进行此步骤前请先确认是否已完成以下步骤：</font><br><a href="/begin/first.html">个人博客第一篇——注册GitHub</a></p></blockquote><p><font size=6><b>Git <font color=red>v2.44.0</font>安装步骤：</b></font></p><h1 id="下载Git"><a href="#下载Git" class="headerlink" title="下载Git"></a><font size=5>下载Git</font></h1><p>  <font size=4>进入Git官方:<a href="https://git-scm.com/">Git官方地址</a>，点击<font color=#49b1f5>Downloads</font></font></p><blockquote><p><img src="/image/second/1.jpg" alt="Git"></p></blockquote><p><font size=4>点击<font color=#49b1f5>Windows</font></font></p><blockquote><p><img src="/image/second/2.jpg" alt="Git"></p></blockquote><p><font size=4>点击<font color=#49b1f5>Click here to download</font>等待下载完成</font></p><blockquote><p><img src="/image/second/3.jpg" alt="Git"></p></blockquote><h1 id="安装Git"><a href="#安装Git" class="headerlink" title=" 安装Git"></a><font size=5> 安装Git</font></h1><p><font size=4>下载完后双击打开，点击next</font></p><blockquote><p><img src="/image/second/4.jpg" alt="Git"></p></blockquote><p><font size=4>选择安装位置</font></p><blockquote><p><img src="/image/second/5.jpg" alt="Git"></p></blockquote><p><font size=4>直接点击next，如果需要创建桌面图标的可以勾选方框</font></p><blockquote><p><img src="/image/second/6.jpg" alt="Git"></p></blockquote><p><font size=4>下面的步骤都默认，点击next</font></p><blockquote><p><img src="/image/second/7.jpg" alt="Git"><br><img src="/image/second/8.jpg" alt="Git"><br><img src="/image/second/9.jpg" alt="Git"><br><img src="/image/second/10.jpg" alt="Git"><br><img src="/image/second/11.jpg" alt="Git"><br><img src="/image/second/12.jpg" alt="Git"><br><img src="/image/second/13.jpg" alt="Git"><br><img src="/image/second/14.jpg" alt="Git"><br><img src="/image/second/15.jpg" alt="Git"><br><img src="/image/second/16.jpg" alt="Git"><br><img src="/image/second/17.jpg" alt="Git"></p></blockquote><p><font size=4>等待安装完成</font></p><blockquote><p><img src="/image/second/18.jpg" alt="Git"></p></blockquote><p><font size=4>安装完成后点击Finish</font></p><blockquote><p><img src="/image/second/19.jpg" alt="Git"></p></blockquote><h1 id="运行Git-Bash"><a href="#运行Git-Bash" class="headerlink" title="运行Git Bash"></a><font size=5>运行Git Bash</font></h1><p><font size=4>完成后鼠标右键空白， 出现如下图所示:</font></p><blockquote><p><img src="/image/second/20.jpg" alt="Git"></p></blockquote><h1 id="检测Git"><a href="#检测Git" class="headerlink" title="检测Git"></a><font size=5>检测Git</font></h1><p><font size=4>打开Git Bash输入<font color=red>git</font>，回车</font></p><blockquote><p><img src="/image/second/21.jpg" alt="Git"></p></blockquote><p><font size=4>回车后弹出如下图所示，则安装成功</font></p><blockquote><p><img src="/image/second/22.jpg" alt="Git"></p></blockquote>]]></content>
      
      
      
